offer_dialogue = "...You found the letter. I knew this day would come. Alright, alright — sit down. I owe you the truth, and I owe it to her, too. That night, the sea was wild, and Cordelia... she said she'd found something beneath the Cove. Something ancient. She walked into the mist and never came back. I've carried that guilt for years."
